AutoCloseable, PooledConnection
public class AutoClosePooledConnection
extends DelegatingPooledConnection<PooledConnection>
implements AutoCloseable, PooledConnection

An AutoCloseable PooledConnection. When the automatic resource management block construct invokes close(), close() will be called on the underlying PooledConnection.
